function_call.name: get_risks
function_call.arguments: {"risks":[{"Description":"Lack of access to legal representation in eviction cases","Impact":"High eviction rates, decreased housing stability, increased spread of contagious diseases","Mitigation":"Implementation of civil right to counsel, provision of universal counsel for income-eligible tenants","Technologies":"Legal aid technology, online counseling platforms","People":"Income-eligible tenants","Owner":"Legal aid organizations, government agencies"},{"Description":"Lack of health care access and medical debt","Impact":"Increased eviction rates, poor health outcomes, decreased ability to seek and maintain employment","Mitigation":"Policies such as Medicaid expansion, reduction of medical debt, increasing health care access","Technologies":"Health care technology, medical debt relief programs","People":"Low-income individuals, tenants","Owner":"Government agencies, health care providers, medical debt relief organizations"}]}
